Select Quantum dot -> Quantum dot Lab â—       Press Launch tool in info section. 
Select the type of Quantum dot Structure â—       Select Energy Bandgap and enter the value â—       Press simulate to view results. 
Select Result - > Energy States 
Repeat the above steps for simple and multi-layer quantum dot â—       Compare the results of various materials. 
  
  
