Â·                Select Tools- Piece-Wise Constant Potential Barriers Sim2L. 
Â·                Press Launch tool in info section. 
Â·                Enter into app mode tab in jupyter environment. 
Â·                Press simulate to view results. 
Â·                Compare the results. 
  
