â—‹ Set up voltage sweeps: 
â–  Gate Voltage Sweep: 
â–  Initial Gate Voltage: 0â€‰V. 
â–  Final Gate Voltage: 1â€‰V. 
â–  Gate Voltage Bias Points: 13. 
â–  Drain Voltage Sweep: 
â–  Initial Drain Voltage: 0â€‰V. 
â–  Final Drain Voltage: 1â€‰V. 
â–  Drain Voltage Bias Points: 13. 
Run the Simulation: 
Click the Simulate button to generate the results. 
Analyze the Output: 
Navigate to the results section: 
â–  View Drain Current vs. Gate Voltage plot. 
